title: Search specific File (mp3,movie,zip,apps) with Google Hacks v.1.
description: Google is a pretty powerful search tool. You knew that. You can use it to find information, but you can also use it to find downloadable MP3s, books, videos, and other items. We&#039;re going to assume you&#039;re just looking for legally available downloads, but the truth of the matter is if someone&#039;s posted an MP3 (copyrighted or not) to their web page, Google can find it.
